  // Content goes here
  .container

    // Navigation Bar (You can copy the navigation bar code from your previous example)

    // Section for "What is IEEE Anurag University?" (added margin-top)
    .section(style='background-color: #87CEEB; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 50px;')
      h2(style='color: #000000;') What is IEEE Anurag University?
      p(style='color: #000000;')
        | IEEE Anurag University Student Chapter is a student branch under the umbrella of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE). It is dedicated to fostering technological innovation and excellence for the benefit of humanity.

    // Section for "Mission"
    .section(style='background-color: #87CEEB; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 10px;')
      h2(style='color: #000000;') Mission
      p(style='color: #000000;')
        | Our mission is to provide a platform for students to explore, learn, and contribute to advancements in technology. We aim to inspire and empower future engineers and leaders.

    // Section for "Vision"
    .section(style='background-color: #87CEEB; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 10px;')
      h2(style='color: #000000;') Vision
      p(style='color: #000000;')
        | Our vision is to be a leading student chapter, driving innovation, collaboration, and positive change. We strive to create a community of passionate individuals making a difference in the world of technology.

    // Section for "About Us"
    .section(style='background-color: #87CEEB; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;')
      h2(style='color: #000000;') About Us
      p(style='color: #000000;')
        | The IEEE Anurag University Student Chapter is comprised of enthusiastic students who are dedicated to promoting the understanding of electrical and electronics engineering. We organize various events, workshops, and activities to enhance the learning experience and create a vibrant community of learners.
